  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventLoopGroupProvider

    public class TestEventLoopGroupProvider
extends DefaultEventLoopGroupProvider
    A EventLoopGroupProvider suitable for testing. Preserves the event loop groups between tests. Every time a new TestEventLoopGroupProvider instance is created, shutdown hook is added Runtime.addShutdownHook(Thread).
